Why CC BY-SA 4.0?

This license embodies the copyleft philosophy: knowledge should be free to 
share and build upon, but improvements must remain free. It's the same 
principle that powers Wikipedia and the open-source movement.

Freedom isn't just about privacy—it's about information too.

– POLYMVTHIC PUNKS